biography: Jari is a rising star from Archipelagia Golf Club, making his mark on the competitive golf scene.  He first graced the fairways of the prestigious Hector Trophée in 2025, showcasing his talent and potential.

While Jari's Hector Trophée appearances have yet to result in a victory, his performances have certainly captured attention.  His consistent play and strategic approach promise a bright future in the world of competitive golf.  The golfing world is eagerly watching Jari's progression and anticipates future successes.
